right skewed signifying the data to be unimodal. Also, right skewness is
proved by the summary obtained in which mean \textgreater{} median of
the departure delay distribution. July in which there is highest average
departure delay of flights from NYC airport. LGA is one of the three
major NYC airports that has a better on time percentage for departing
flights. Plane with tail number N666DN having the highest average speed.
27.40\% of the flights arrived on time though departed late.
